metadata.name: Aus DeFi NFT Heroes - Degen
metadata.description:
What comes to mind when you say ‘degen’? Think of your stereotypes, this girl has them all. ETH earrings? Check. Vampiric sleeping and working patterns? Check. Extensive hoodie collection? Check. The Degen is forging a life that is entirely anonymised. No fiat bank account, no bank card, no car, no drivers licence. The Degen uses a different burner phone every week. You can only speak to her on Telegram and Signal. She’s in every yield farming protocol Discord out there. She laughs at the idea of “taxes” and every second word is an expletive. We’re not even sure of her nationality. She loves a cheeky vape and she has put out a hit contract on Gary Gensler - I think it’s with Russians. Her favourite TV show is The Last Airbender. She came second at the World Degen Games on Avalanche in September 2022, winning 15,000 BUSD. Of course, they were immediately dropped into Bearn.fi

For more info on Aus DeFi Association check out our homepage www.defi.org.au
